 interplay between\nmagnetic orders and optical excitations in vdW magnetic materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2020 19:23:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Jun 2020 14:19:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-01"}
