ficant reduction in the number of\niterations and improved stability with respect to problem nonlinearity, mesh\nrefinement, and the polynomial order of the discretization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2020 21:07:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2020 17:42:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
