ons to stem the spread of cheating and\nantisocial behavior more generally in online communities, schools,\norganizations, and sports.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2020 22:38:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Jan 2022 14:45:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-28"}
