ost blobs are not connecting\nto the divertor plates and suggest that they are generated by the shearing of\nthe turbulent modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Mar 2020 04:28:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
